Package org.statcato.dialogs.stat.nonparametrics

Provides classes for dialogs pertaining to nonparametric statistics.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    KruskalWallisDialog
    A dialog for the Kruskal-Wallis Test
    MatchedPairSignTestDialog
    A dialog for the matched-pair sign test (distribution-free, two-sample).
    RankCorrelationDialog
    A dialog for Spearman's rank correlation.
    RunsTestDialog
    A dialog for Spearman's rank correlation.
    SignTestDialog
    A dialog for the sign test (distribution-free, one-sample).
    WilcoxonRankSumTestDialog  
    WilcoxonSignedRankTestDialog
    A dialog for Wilcoxon signed rank test for one sample or two samples of matched pairs.
